##################
Vagrant VM Manager
##################

A thin layer to manage your vagrant virtual machine.

USAGE
=====

 1. Configure the settings.py file
 2. Use vm script :

    $ vm download
    $ vm start my_vm
    $ vm stop my_vm

COMMANDS
========

 - start vm_name
 - stop vm_name
 - download
 - configure vm_name
 - reconfigure vm_name
 - delete vm_name
 - ssh vm_name
 - restart vm_name
